Semilocal Reflected-Packet Oscillation
Version 1.0.2, 23 July 2026

This repository is a standalone research and reproducibility artifact for
the fixed-packet reflected-interaction theorem.

The source research files from which this repository was assembled did not
contain an explicit licensing policy. Accordingly, this repository does not
add an open-source license or grant permissions that were not present in the
source material. No LICENSE file is intentionally supplied.

External mathematical sources are cited in paper/main.tex and in the
research notes. Their copyrights and licensing terms remain with their
respective authors and publishers. No external paper is redistributed here.

The numerical outputs are diagnostics. They are not part of the
load-bearing analytic proof and do not constitute a proof of the Riemann
hypothesis.
